{
  "stem": "22660.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He knew not to be home at that point, right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knew not to be home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And ultimately, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they almost caught him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a very scary, scary thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can tell you the story how that happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was alone in my apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was writing letters to a friend of mine who had already immigrated to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my grandparents lived downstairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Gestapo came to my house, they said-- they gave me a push.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said [SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no, I said, I can swear that he isn't home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If Jews give their word, that's no word at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave me a push and I fell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they ransacked the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while they were doing that, I went down the servants' entrance to, to go downstairs to my grandparents where my father was, and whispered, they're upstairs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with that-- the car of the Gestapo was outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So with that, my grandmother was like-- very late at night-- my grandmother took my father, and they left through the servants' door, walked by the car of the Gestapo, and went to a doctor that was a Catholic doctor, who gave my father some kind of a certificate.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- my father was-- First World War, '14-'18, he was in the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had the Iron Cross, and he had things that were wrong still from the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he really hadn't suffered from those at this point anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this nice doctor gave him a certificate and told him-- got him into a Catholic hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
